Class Summary 
Class Description
ClackClient
A class that represents a client user.
ClackData
An abstract Class representing data sent between a client and a server
ClackServer
Class for hosting clack service
ClientSideServerListener
A class responsible for receiving data from the server and printing it parallel to the ClackClient Class.
FileClackData
A Class, inheriting from ClackData, that represents the contents of a file.
MessageClackData
A Class, inheriting from ClackData, for messages being sent
ServerSideClientIO
A class that handles sending and receiving data, as long as the connection is open.
TestClackClient
A class to test ClackClient.

TestClackServer
A Class for testing ClackServer
